Java Program to perform Array Operations:

I am taking Scanner class from util package.
 firstly, I have created a default class named ArrayOperations.
I have defined the main method to begin the execution.
I am defining the Scanner class to take input from the user.
I am asking user to enter number of rows and number of columns into the array
I am reading the values and inputing into the array.
I am creating two arrays for rows and columns.
After that, I am displaying the sum of each row of a matrix 
The highest sum among all rows in a matrix and 
Sum of all columns and 
The highest sum among all columns in a matrix 
finally, I am displaying The highest sum among all columns in a matrix
